CHO好像已经把Dr.Bruce Aylward的页面从CHO网站中重定向。可能迫于国际压力吧😂<br>
<br>
Tellingly, Dr.Bruce Aylward has since been removed from the WHO website, his webpage (<a href="https://www.who.int/dg/adg/aylward/en/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">www.who.int/dg/adg/aylward/en/</a>) now redirects to the general leadership team page, which lists no mention of him.&nbsp;
